file.name: all_of.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Entities
  version: "1.0"
paths:
  /:
    get:
      operationId: getRoot
      responses:
        "200":
          description: ""
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Dog"
components:
  schemas:
    Dog:
      allOf:
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/Animal"
        - type: object
          properties:
            breed:
              type: string
    Animal:
      type: object
      required:
        - className
      properties:
        className:
          type: string
        color:
          type: string
          default: red
      additionalProperties: true
